" Remap Caps lock
imap <C-a> <Esc>
vmap <C-a> <Esc>

" Case-insensitive searching.
set ignorecase

" But case-sensitive if expression contains a capital letter.
set smartcase

" Default to global substitutions on lines
set gdefault

" Move between assistant editors
nnoremap <C-j> <C-w>j
nnoremap <C-k> <C-w>k
nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l
nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h

" Comment & uncomment
nnoremap <Space>c :xccmd commentAndUncommentCurrentLines<CR>
vnoremap <Space>c :xccmd commentAndUncommentCurrentLines<CR>

" Edit in scope
nnoremap <Space>e :xccmd toggleTokenizedEditing<CR>

" Open quickly
nnoremap <Space>t :xccmd openQuickly<CR>

" Open & close assistant
nnoremap <Space>v <C-w>n :xccmd openQuickly<CR>
nnoremap <Space>w <C-w>q

" Indent selection
nnoremap <Space>i ==

" Open navigator
nnoremap <Space>n :xccmd toggleNavigatorsVisibility<CR>
